Flowchart

Start
Generate a random number
Genearte blanks equal to the letters in a word
Ask the user to guess letters
Is the guessed letter in the word?
If yes:
Replace the blank with the letter
Then,
Are all the blanks filled?
If Yes,
Game Over
If No,
Go back to line 6.

Now, If No , #From Line 7
Lose a life
Then,
Have they run out of lives?
If Yes, 
Game over

If No, 
Return to Line 6.
